Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.44,0:00:09.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Kagami Yoshimizu Theater"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.91,0:00:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3rd year, class B...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.08,0:00:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kuroi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.20,0:00:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The ambiguous 3cm? Does that \Nmean it's plushy? Wait!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.40,0:00:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The wrapping is a uniform, \Nargh, it's not an act, pooh{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.58,0:00:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gotta do your best, gotta just do it{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.29,0:00:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's time to catch 'n' release, eek{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.91,0:00:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Between sweat (whoop) Sweat (whoop){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.95,0:00:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Darlin', darlin', freeze! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.59,0:00:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kinda lethargic, something's kinda comin' out{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.91,0:00:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I love you... Oh wait, one \Nof those was different{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.92,0:00:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Worrywarts, high metal bars {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.12,0:00:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tasty thoughts... And that's enough!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.91,0:00:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The heated body of that flying you-know-who{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.70,0:00:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's what you call a normal girlie{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.22,0:00:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Am I the only one surprised? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.62,0:00:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seconds on pork-bone broth \Nramen with wire-hard noodles{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.77,0:00:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Da da da da da {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.94,0:00:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pom-poms cheer squad{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.66,0:00:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's get cherry pie {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.37,0:00:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Happy fun welcoming party {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.01,0:00:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Look up! Sensation{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.45,0:00:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah! Feeling of existence, \Ndot dot small planet{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.41,0:00:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Collided and it melted away, in total awe{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.08,0:01:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go all out to sing, shi-ranger!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.97,0:01:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Take it away! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.00,0:01:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I should be the one who'll \Nbe laughing in the end{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.50,0:01:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because I have the sailor suit \N← This is my conclusion{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.51,0:01:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's only Monday! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.70,0:01:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Already in a bad mood? What to do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.45,0:01:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I really prefer the summer outfits \N← kya! Wah! Good! (cute!) < 3{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Until we approach 3 pixels, \Nno hesitations please ★{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.34,0:01:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do your best, be energetic {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.02,0:01:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My darlin', darlin' please! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.03,0:01:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.86,0:01:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S'up?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.15,0:01:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.41,0:01:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You remembered to wear the winter uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.62,0:01:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm no Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.54,0:01:43.24,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.24,0:01:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's still hot out,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.41,0:01:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I think we could've stayed in \Nour summer uniforms a bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.92,0:01:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when we swap to the summer \Nones, it's still cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.29,0:01:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really wish that they'd let us \Nchoose on our own when to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.80,0:01:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.80,0:01:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's mostly trying to get \Nus to change gears, mentally.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.05,0:02:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, we'd end up with people \Nwho are less clear-cut, like you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.72,0:02:03.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Pandora's Box"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.97,0:02:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our family isn't like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.27,0:02:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I hear that some parents \Nout there check out the e-mail
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.77,0:02:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on their daughters' cell \Nphones and computers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.81,0:02:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I hear about that every once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.02,0:02:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't happen with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.24,0:02:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that happens here, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.47,0:02:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your dad loves you to death,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.61,0:02:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so he wouldn't do anything that \Nhis daughter would dislike, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.45,0:02:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there's that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.11,0:02:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But my dad uses computers, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.04,0:02:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, he probably knows it's humiliating \Nwhen someone peeks at your D drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.71,0:02:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.44,0:02:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summer was so full of classes and stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.55,0:02:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that the only play time I had was \Nwhen we went to see the fireworks,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.18,0:02:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that time in Ariake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.72,0:02:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you went to Comiket after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.85,0:02:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Comiket...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.64,0:02:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to that, my wallet \Nis feeling a bit lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.64,0:02:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just how much did you spend there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.64,0:02:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really cut loose there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.69,0:02:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each volume cost an average \Nof 1,000 yen each...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.87,0:02:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I think somewhere around \N40,000 to 50,000 yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.07,0:02:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.07,0:02:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are limits as to how much your \Nfinancial outlook can be warped...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.90,0:03:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You say that, Kagamin, but "fair \Nmarket value" exists in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.91,0:03:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Self-published items are \Nrelatively expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not talking about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.45,0:03:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about your mental state, \Nspending so much money on them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.91,0:03:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whew.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.28,0:03:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still hot out, though \Nit's already September.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.04,0:03:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.75,0:03:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that it's especially \Nhot out this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.30,0:03:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're talking about \Nglobal warming and such.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.21,0:03:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yu-{\i1}chan {\i0}can get heat \Nexhaustion really easily,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.68,0:03:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so she often rests in the living \Nroom and other rooms with A/C.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.93,0:03:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa always spends her time in \Nrooms with air conditioning, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.51,0:03:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though she's just slacking off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.51,0:03:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Dad and I join her, \Nand we always roll around,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.36,0:03:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the shape of the kanji "shou (small)."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.65,0:03:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Shou?" By that, don't \Nyou mean "kawa (river)?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.74,0:03:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Dad always lies down in the middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.68,0:03:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your house is always like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.04,0:03:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess Yutaka-{\i1}chan {\i0}has gotten used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.42,0:03:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoo-hoo! Yutaka, are you doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:03:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to visit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.09,0:04:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Who might this be?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.05,0:04:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my friend, Minami Iwasaki-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this is the Minami-{\i1}chan {\i0}that \Nyou always talk about, Yutaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.02,0:04:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.69,0:04:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a little bit jealous,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.23,0:04:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with so much hope coming from \Nsomeone that is closest to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.40,0:04:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I've heard many a rumor, \Nbut you really are pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm totally surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.34,0:04:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want something to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.62,0:04:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, beer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.16,0:04:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Didn't you drive here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.54,0:04:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding! Barley tea. Barley tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.08,0:04:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see... one sibling absorbed \Nthat of the other... absorbed...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.56,0:04:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it was just the {\i1}yassai-mossai {\i0}festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.60,0:04:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always get so sleepy at night. \NIs there a good way to avoid it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.32,0:05:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it better to just go to sleep \Nearly and wake up early in the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,instead of forcing yourself to \Ngo on? You'd feel better too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.42,0:05:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.43,0:05:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wake up a bit early, and do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.06,0:05:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Why is it the same \Ntime as usual right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.92,0:05:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, I remember stopping \Nsomething somewhere in the middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.09,0:05:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of my old habits, \Neven if I get up early,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel reassured and fall asleep again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.13,0:05:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So weak-willed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.86,0:05:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's better for me to do my best \Nand keep going late into the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.51,0:05:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get better results if you're \Nrubbing sleepy eyes the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.60,0:05:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, why don't you \Nhave someone wake you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.56,0:05:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom and the others wake up early.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.78,0:05:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes. I'll make sure to get you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.40,0:05:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, this will definitely work. \NNothing less from you, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom! I told you to wake me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.21,0:05:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did wake you up, and you answered me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.88,0:06:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? I don't know anything about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.05,0:06:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.13,0:06:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis forgot her lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.52,0:06:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hallway of a different \Ngraduating class seems so strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.53,0:06:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I'm under some pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.61,0:06:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Yu-{\i1}chan {\i0}really got some attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, she looks like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.87,0:06:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's usually just you overreacting, \Nbut upper or underclassmen aside,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.42,0:06:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,going to a different place \Ncreates a strange atmosphere
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.92,0:06:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that makes you feel like you're \Nthe center of attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.30,0:06:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm small to begin with, so I stand out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.01,0:06:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when I think upperclassmen are \Nlooking at me, I really feel pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.85,0:06:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I rather like getting that kind of attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.31,0:06:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.14,0:07:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even if I go into the 10th graders' area,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.08,0:07:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get much attention,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.25,0:07:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,since they don't think I'm an upperclassman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.27,0:07:04.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Doesn't give off the feeling \Nof an upperclassman"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Patty-{\i1}chan{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.61,0:07:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi! Nice to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.86,0:07:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to work now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.95,0:07:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I put in too \Nmany shifts this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still going on with that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.84,0:07:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. We're pretty popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.29,0:07:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The A-Boys are all {\i1}moe-moe {\i0}for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.38,0:07:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you call the boys that \Nlook like they are {\i1}that {\i0}type,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.42,0:07:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the ones that often are found in Akiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.34,0:07:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Narimiya-{\i1}kun {\i0}was a bit different.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.97,0:07:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotten quite accustomed to Japan now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.60,0:07:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though only in one particular point!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.39,0:07:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I came up with a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.48,0:07:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I get out of the \Nbath, I'll sketch it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... I can't remember what it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.33,0:07:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This always happens when I don't \Njot down a note right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.62,0:08:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was so amusing! I know \Nit was really amusing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.96,0:08:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tired today too...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.46,0:08:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this idea may be a bit amusing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.63,0:08:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll sketch it out when I \Nget up tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.35,0:08:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That's strange... What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.35,0:08:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it was a wonderful idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.69,0:08:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I wrote a memo to myself, \Ninstead of feeling too lazy to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.45,0:08:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, geez! I even woke up right away! \NWhy do I forget dreams so easily?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.66,0:08:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so positive that it was an amusing idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.46,0:08:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lucky Star{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.76,0:08:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, all of you, talk it \Nout and make up your minds!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.87,0:08:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we're going all the \Nway out to Kyoto and Nara,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:08:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,look up those tourist spots \Nthat you feel will be the bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.37,0:09:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't we going to hit all the \Ntourist spots together by bus?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.68,0:09:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The places we're all going \Ntogether are so standard-fare
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.98,0:09:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that it won't be any fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.77,0:09:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you say that, you take \Nall the fun out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.97,0:09:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Iris went inside here...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.54,0:09:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I'd like to give you a tour \Nof the ancient capital of Nara.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.04,0:09:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has been about 1300 years since \Nthe relocation of the capital
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.71,0:09:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to Kyoto, back in the year \N710 of the Heian era.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.04,0:09:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please enjoy the historical dramas from Nara,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drama that you can nar-row down \Nas events specific to Nara.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.14,0:09:42.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Nar-row down to Nara! - \NNar-row down to Nara! -
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.51,0:09:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this where you're supposed to laugh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.86,0:09:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the main body, and all \Nthe little ones around it are...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.48,0:09:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...options!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.74,0:09:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, you'll get divine \Npunishment for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.64,0:10:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all sticky.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.14,0:10:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smelly! I'm all smelly now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.77,0:10:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.27,0:10:30.27,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,It's rather smelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.27,0:10:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.23,0:10:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he means, "Please \Npush the shutter for us."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.34,0:10:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.91,0:10:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Click, click.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.78,0:10:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.66,0:10:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At times like this, how much \Nyou usually study really shows.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like you can talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.12,0:10:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.87,0:10:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, how do you say "Cheese!" in India?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.17,0:10:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean, in Hindi? Let's see, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.58,0:11:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, even the genius Kagami is at a loss!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.84,0:11:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, don't they understand \NEnglish in India as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.14,0:11:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I think "Say \Ncheese!" should be good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.42,0:11:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.81,0:11:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say cheese!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.77,0:11:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, on these study tours, a lot \Nof couples suddenly start dating.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.32,0:11:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The events during the study tour are a must.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.32,0:11:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, I believe that the environment
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.28,0:11:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,outside the school grounds \Nmakes you feel more open.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.99,0:11:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's the time that \Nyou feel is the right time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.29,0:11:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's rather embarrassing, but \NI can't settle down and sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.54,0:11:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when I have to use a different pillow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.25,0:11:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's rather embarrassing, but \NI can't settle down and sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.38,0:11:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when I don't have this next to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.09,0:11:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's rather embarrassing, \Nbut if I don't turn this on
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.26,0:11:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at least once a day, I can't \Nsettle down and sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.39,0:11:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, the bus will soon \Narrive at Kiyomizu Temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.64,0:11:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hill leading up to Kiyomizu Temple \Nis called the Three-Year Hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.69,0:11:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Legend has it that if you trip here, \Nyou will die in three years' time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.36,0:12:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Three-Year Hill (sannen-zaka) \NTurns into Sorry Hill (zannen-zaka).
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.76,0:12:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that include laughing to death?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.06,0:12:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up! We're starting \Nthe group activities now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.41,0:12:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Walk around, but be careful \Nof cars around you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to meet back up in \Nfront of Chioin Temple at 12:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.41,0:12:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.92,0:12:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone who's late has a 20-page \Nreport in their future!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.62,0:12:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.61,0:12:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.60,0:12:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe this is about how heavy \Nthat Dragon Slayer was?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.06,0:12:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is so high up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.60,0:12:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say, "Feeling as if you were \Njumping off the Kiyomizu stage,"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.20,0:12:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if you really were to jump \Noff from here, wouldn't you die?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.78,0:12:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So do they mean it doesn't \Nmatter what happens afterwards?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.07,0:12:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagamin, you have no dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.71,0:12:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, it's a god of romance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.82,0:12:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, this is a very famous \Ngod for bringing couples together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.45,0:12:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So easy to understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.08,0:12:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, see, they have love fortunes over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.08,0:12:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all pick fortunes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.58,0:12:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, let's do it, let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.42,0:13:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected, I can't figure \Nout which is which.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.84,0:13:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.20,0:13:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.85,0:13:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"♪78 Great blessings"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Great blessings!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.06,0:13:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, I'm jealous, Kona-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.43,0:13:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I was just fortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's really good enough. Now, as for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.82,0:13:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"♪7 Half-blessing"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.33,0:13:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Half-blessing? What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.61,0:13:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it means you're half-blessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.90,0:13:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, you're half cursed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.28,0:13:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could care less about love fortunes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.95,0:13:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.66,0:13:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.54,0:13:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Kagami, I think this one's for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.63,0:13:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.42,0:13:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to buy this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.45,0:13:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami, Kagami, you forgot. You forgot this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not buying it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.51,0:13:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what about this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't buy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.74,0:13:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, be more careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.31,0:14:00.11,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Devotional tablets to fulfill romance"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:14:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that says, "Konata is my wife."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.58,0:14:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, is everyone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.98,0:14:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to the hotel now \Nto have lunch. Let's get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, when you're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.03,0:14:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was written that Koizumi's \Ncharacter song was sung IZAM-style.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.33,0:14:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.33,0:14:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have someone following us from behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.91,0:14:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.38,0:14:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, it will be \NHokkaido all over again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.24,0:14:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to say, "___tel!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.17,0:14:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot! 50-page report for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.05,0:14:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Driver, excuse me! Please stop the bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.72,0:14:36.22,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hotel Honnouji"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.22,0:14:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.56,0:14:40.94,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"To Hiiragi"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.07,0:14:50.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"I want to talk to you, so please meet me at 9 PM in \Nfront of the hotel we're staying at. --From a certain boy"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.29,0:15:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kinkaku Temple is golden, but \NGinkaku Temple isn't silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.83,0:15:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's brought up as a pair with Kinkaku,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.42,0:15:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they named it "Gin (silver)" \Nto complement "Kin (gold)."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.76,0:15:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, it wasn't meant to \Nbe silver to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.18,0:15:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if they don't have Sapphire \Nor Ruby, like they do in {\i1}Pok_mon{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.64,0:15:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'd capture...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.74,0:15:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our shrine was in the news the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.66,0:15:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only one day left now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.07,0:15:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got our free activity plans down pat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.78,0:15:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow is our true study tour!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.07,0:15:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onward, to the sanctuary!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.03,0:15:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.64,0:15:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said in front of the hotel... \NWas this the right place?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.76,0:15:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Were you waiting long?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.18,0:16:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what did you want to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.91,0:16:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I can't say this to \Nanyone but you, Hiiragi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.87,0:16:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to give me that doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.26,0:16:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.08,0:16:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, the one you bought at the \Nsouvenir shop at Kiyomizu Temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.56,0:16:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The little Yatsuhashi doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.92,0:16:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Yatsuhashi-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, that's the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.68,0:16:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really took a liking to \Nit, and I really want one,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.43,0:16:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't know what everyone would say
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.56,0:16:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if anyone saw someone like me buying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.31,0:16:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.27,0:16:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.44,0:16:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks! I owe you one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And don't tell anyone about this, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.24,0:17:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. That story about \Nbrothers that turn into dragons...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.20,0:17:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was it called?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.91,0:17:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean {\i1}Sohryuden{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.79,0:17:06.17,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! That! I'd like to see the \Nanime for that, if they ever...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.79,0:17:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.17,0:17:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The steam inside has cooled down, \Nand created a small vacuum.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.00,0:17:11.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,They released an OVA for \Nit quite a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.25,0:17:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you slightly slide one end,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.96,0:17:15.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that so? I didn't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.38,0:17:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Air will enter and make it easier \Nfor you to take the lid off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.09,0:17:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.09,0:17:18.34,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Though it only goes to \Nvolume 4 or so of the...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.34,0:17:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, those books...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.85,0:17:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.31,0:17:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure put on a show, even to the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.57,0:17:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I totally did the background \Nresearch for the location.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.18,0:17:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we really go there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.15,0:17:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, we're only going to look \Nat the building from the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.16,0:17:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to go this far just \Nbecause you're in Kyoto, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.39,0:17:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't understand the marron \Nof being an otaku at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.29,0:17:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nor do I ever want to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.67,0:17:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.59,0:17:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just about right, so that \Nthey can concentrate on their work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.33,0:18:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The building is a lot more normal \Nthan I thought it would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.48,0:18:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They keep the number of titles \Nsmall, so this is just about right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.81,0:18:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you have to come all the \Nway to Kyoto to buy that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.49,0:18:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! That's so embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.86,0:18:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. Think of \Nit as a memory of this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.62,0:18:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take a picture together, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.33,0:18:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will be for memory's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.08,0:18:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, we came all the way out to Kyoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.46,0:18:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What part of this is like Kyoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.78,0:18:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Tsukasa and I are both back, just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.89,0:18:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa is already asleep, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.06,0:18:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that you'd be asleep \Nalready from frustration, Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.60,0:18:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I be asleep from frustration?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.40,0:18:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you stick that Print \NClub sticker somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.48,0:18:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I'd be able to stick \Nthat embarrassing thing anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.97,0:19:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That embarrassing thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.87,0:19:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We had our study tour this \Nweek, so I really worked hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.63,0:19:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, this weekend, since it's been a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.36,0:19:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll play my heart out on 'net games!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.88,0:19:18.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Announcement of emergency maintenance"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.39,0:19:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lucky Star{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.87,0:19:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lucky Channel{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.13,0:19:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning Luckies!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.62,0:19:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, I have another booming \Ninstallment of {\i1}Lucky Channel{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.61,0:19:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Akira Kogami, your navigator!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.69,0:19:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm Daisuke Ono, the assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.73,0:19:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time passes by so quickly, and \Nwe're already on episode 21!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.24,0:19:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. We're finally \Ngetting to the final stages.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.91,0:19:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's hurry on towards this segment...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.74,0:19:47.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"This Week's Maggare"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.49,0:19:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Week's Maggare...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.41,0:19:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh... Who is that? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.58,0:19:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've scooped some up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.68,0:20:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sniff sniff...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.80,0:20:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this? It's lukewarm!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.88,0:20:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't possibly drink something like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.23,0:20:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, I'd rather drink \Nsomething from a vending machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.15,0:20:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.65,0:20:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You! {\i1}You{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just how much of your antics \Ndo you think I've put up with?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.26,0:20:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You always, {\i1}always {\i0}have \Nnothing but selfish requests!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.03,0:20:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minoru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.33,0:20:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, of all days, will be \Nthe day I break it to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.41,0:20:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how I've felt each week \Nwhen I was doing this segment?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.58,0:20:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I spent day after day working \Npart-time at Ko_____hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.79,0:20:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I make more part-time than \NI do as a voice actor!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.29,0:20:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And thanks to that, I'm one \Nof the veteran employees!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.59,0:20:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before I lift your spirits every week, \NI'm frying up ground meat cutlets!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.13,0:20:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you are better suited for that occupation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.43,0:20:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.76,0:20:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you sitting there \Nin the first place, Ono?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.43,0:20:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That seat's reserved for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.06,0:20:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have been cut out of the loop \Nby the producer and director.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.06,0:20:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.00,0:21:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're too quick to come to judgment!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.32,0:21:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the type that matures late in the game!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.94,0:21:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can instantly turn into \Na Starga__r from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.28,0:21:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can someone like you really do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.95,0:21:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're mocking me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.33,0:21:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't keep going with someone like \NHi__mosu, or with Lo__-and-__rry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.21,0:21:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.13,0:21:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to quit this show, goddammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.26,0:21:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about {\i1}Lucky Channel{\i0}, dammit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.93,0:21:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you filming me for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.89,0:21:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about {\i1}Misoji Misaki {\i0}({\i1}Cape Thirties{\i0})?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.31,0:21:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If something like that can be \Na comic idea, I'll admit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.89,0:21:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm almost 30!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.48,0:21:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I'm ever going to forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.86,0:21:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to Idaho!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.61,0:21:49.95,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"His belt isn't long enough, so he has \Nsomeone holding it behind his back."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.95,0:21:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there, I'm Minoru Shiraishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.28,0:21:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I'll have you listen up! \N{\i1}- Song of Shikaidar{\i0}, boom!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.45,0:21:55.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.05,0:22:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.97,0:22:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.07,0:22:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.45,0:22:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.81,0:22:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you had enough of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.98,0:22:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shikaidar is... Shikaidar is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.85,0:23:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stutter!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.36,0:23:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is a cyborg!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.40,0:23:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until the day evil is obliterated, \Nhe will continue to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.57,0:23:06.60,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,You've had enough, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.99,0:23:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't fight like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.03,0:23:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.86,0:23:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously no good. You'll have to do it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.57,0:23:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.37,0:23:16.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Next Episode Preview"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.37,0:23:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what's up with the \Nnext episode of {\i1}Lucky Star{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.08,0:23:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akira Kogami here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.37,0:23:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daisuke Ono here. Caw.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.83,0:23:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pekko? Pekko. Pekko pekko pekko.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.96,0:23:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Caw, caw.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.09,0:23:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pekko?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.13,0:23:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Caw caw.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.13,0:23:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pekko!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.88,0:23:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Caw.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.51,0:23:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, that's enough of the animal talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.05,0:23:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so those were animals?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.26,0:23:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: The Yonder Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.77,0:23:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can cross the finish line, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.52,0:23:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pekko!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.06,0:23:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A ramen set!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.15,0:23:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
